        "content": "<p>Is it possible to split a goal of the form <code>A∧B∧C∧...∧H</code> in subgoals <code>A, B, ..., H</code> with a single tactic?</p>",
        "id": 201612783,
        "sender_full_name": "Nicolò Cavalleri",
        "timestamp": 1592836328
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><code>refine \\&lt; _, _, _, _ \\&gt;</code></p>",
        "id": 201612880,
        "sender_full_name": "Johan Commelin",
        "timestamp": 1592836371
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Or maybe <code>repeat { split }</code>?</p>",
